IP-адрес машин
nano /etc/network/interfaces

ISP:
auto ens3
iface ens3 inet static
address 10.0.173.2/24
gateway 10.0.173.11
auto ens4
iface ens4 inet static
address 11.11.11.1/30
auto ens5
iface ens5 inet static
address 22.22.22.1/30
auto ens6
iface ens6 inet static
address 33.33.33.1/30

